Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]] [[gonyaina tsazamakonya]] (Rectangle) chiumbwa chine makonya mana ose akaenzana; gonya rimwe nerimwe rakakura kuita 90<sup>o</sup>. Mativi maviri akatarisana anenge akaenzana uye akati sambamba. Tsazano rinogona kupinda mubandiko rechiumbwa ichi asi kazhinji tinosarudza kuti tsazana rimire roga.
